---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Title from "../components/Title.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="m-auto max-w-4xl mb-20 md:mb-0">
    <a href="/">
      <h1
        transition:name="title"
        class="font-black uppercase text-6xl md:text-8xl text-center py-8 dark:text-white"
      >
        About
      </h1>
    </a>
    <p
      class="dark:text-white dark:font-light text-xl md:text-2xl w-full font-normal text-black mb-20 p-8"
    >
      I created this web app while I was learning astro watching a youtube
      tutorial from midudev where we created the index and the book pages, back
      then the app only had our review of the books. After finishing the
      tutorial I decided to continue working on the project adding more things
      and turning it into a books reviews page for everyone.
      <br />
      <br />
      Now, I¬¥ve always been a fan of reading and been to places like goodreads or
      other review sites that were a little to much for me in terms UX, don¬¥t get
      me wrong they are good sites, I just like simplicty and that¬¥s why I decided
      to create this project to provide just that: An easy way for readers to find
      new books, write reviews and follow their progress as they read through a book.
      <br />
      <br />
      The first version of this site will be quite basic and I will continue to update
      it to provide a more complete app.
      <br />
      <br />
      This is created with so much love and dedication. Feel free to provide feedback
      on what you would like to see on the site, see you soon üòÅ.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/img/reading.svg"
      alt="Reading Ilustration"
      class="md:w-1/2 md:h-1/2 w-3/4 h-3/4 m-auto"
    />
  </main>
</Layout>
